bazel --host_jvm_args="-Xms512m" --host_jvm_args="-Xmx1024m" test \

    --test_timeout 300,450,1200,3600 --build_tests_only \

log available at : http://ci.tensorflow.org/job/tensorflow-contrib-s390x/1516/console

Is there any way to find out which component pulls boringssl?
